flowchart TD
  P0["sync_auto_graph (FrameGraph)"]
  P1["collect target sizes and surface views"]
  P2["for each realm invocation in frame order"]
  P3["sync scene from realm and universal resources"]
  P4["sync camera targets and projection"]
  P5["prepare_render"]
  P6["execute Graph3D passes"]
  P7["compose realm output into target layer"]
  P8["compose target to window"]
  P9["present swapchain image"]

  P0 --> P1
  P1 --> P2
  P2 --> P3
  P3 --> P4
  P4 --> P5
  P5 --> P6
  P6 --> P7
  P7 --> P8
  P8 --> P9

  PASS["Typical Graph3D chain: shadow -> depth_prepass -> skybox -> forward -> outline -> ssao -> bloom -> post"]
  MAT["Material path: definition + instance -> composer -> compiled program cache"]

  P6 --> PASS
  P5 --> MAT
